#DogecoinToTheMoon 🌎🚀🌝

#DogecoinToTheMoon 🌎🚀🌝
When the entire country is divided, there is one thing that has brought liberals, conservatives, black, white, left and right together. That’s #Dogecoin!
@AlexjFerraro I own both, but I guarantee it’s Doge. The world just found out what Dogecoin is, and most of them still never heard of Etherium.

We just experienced a significant crypto market crash of around 20% last night and despite owning ~25 different cryptos, I have gained value on the back of two coins everyone told me not to buy:
#Dogecoin & #Safemoon

Dogecoin haters can’t admit that thus far they’ve been absolutely wrong. And BECAUSE they were wrong, they will continue to be wrong long into the future. #Doge has established itself as the OG meme coin. That value will never subside. Ya’ll lost this one, go home.

I know few will believe me. But I’m a praying man. Earlier this year God pointed me toward #Dogecoin and I went all in despite the expert advice. 

I’m glad to report that once again, God wins. And he ain’t done yet!

I don’t think people understand what’s about to happen to the crypto world because of Doge. The average American has no idea what #Etherium is, but they know #Bitcoin and Dogecoin. 

The next few years will ROCK the crypto world, and #Dogecoin will have the last laugh.
I believe Dogecoin will surpass Etherium’s market cap as #2 crypto currency in the world. How soon? Can’t say yet, but sooner than we’d ever expect.

If the crypto “experts” you listen to are currently mocking #Dogecoin, they are in fact not experts at all. 

I recommend you find yourself someone who has invested and profited from #Doge to find out how they knew. They likely can tip you off on other cryptos too.
